This logical model cannot be the target of a reference
patient 1..1BackboneElementpatient data
fibricheckUserId 1..1stringuser id
niss_number 1..1stringPatient NISS Number
userName 1..1HumanNameuser name
userEmail 1..1stringapp version
dateOfBirth 1..1dateDate of Birth
status 1..1codeMeasurement status
measurementTimeStamp 1..1dateTimeMeasurement timestamp
heartRhythm 0..1BackboneElementheart rhythm
hr-indicator 0..1codethe result of the finding and review
Binding: Heart Rate Indicator Value Set (required)
hrReviewFinding 0..1codethe finding after review
Binding: Heart Rate Finding Value Set (required)
rmssd 0..1decimalrmssd value
context 0..1BackboneElementcontext during a finding
symptoms 0..*codesymptoms
Binding: Context findings Value Set (required)
activityStatus 0..1codeactivity status
Binding: Context Activity Value Set (required)
chadsvasc 0..*codeprevious chadsvasc questions and score
reports 0..1BackboneElementreports
eventReport 0..1Attachmentevent report
aggregatedReport 0..1AttachmentAggregated report
capture 0..1BackboneElementcapture data
measurementAttempts 1..1integerMeasurement attempts
appVersion 1..1stringapp version
